jonathandturner bumped Nu to the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1937] latest rustyline
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1921] more deps
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1920] more deps
. Also moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1919] commands off of async_stream!
 ( 
